rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Welcome, mo! Even if you are friends
of Rex, Meroro not give any freebies,
mo! Meroro drive a hard bargain, mo!

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, welcome back, Rex, mo! You
are always welcome here, mo!

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The lineup for salvage buybacks
changes subtly, mo. It is good
to check in frequently, mo.

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0004
rows.name:
You are so diligent, mo. Meroro
wish my layabout son would learn
from your example, mo.

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Rex, it's been a while, mo.
Lately, Hiyokkoo is the one who
shows his face the most, mo.

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0006
rows.name:
People really do grow, mo...
Unlike my layabout son, who
does not grow at all, mo.

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Even with Alst in such a crisis,
surprisingly, my layabout son
does not leave the house, mo.

rows.label: tlk006001_01_msg0008
rows.name:
Once Alst is at peace, Meroro want
to make him Rex's apprentice, mo.
Please take care of him, mo!
